```dockerfile
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates

RUN wget -O /tmp/rds-ca.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-bundle -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca.pem

RUN wget -O /tmp/digicert.crt https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-azure -file /tmp/digicert.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/digicert.crt

RUN addgroup -S appgroup && adduser -S app -G appgroup
USER app

COPY --from=builder /app/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java Analytics Dashboard"

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
